<h3 class="heading"><span class="type">Paragraph</span></h3>
<p>With this in mind, we want to find <span class="process-math">\(y\)</span> when <span class="process-math">\(\dfdx{y}{t}=0\)</span> (how high), <span class="process-math">\(t\)</span> when <span class="process-math">\(y=0\)</span> (when it hits the ground), and <span class="process-math">\(\eval{\dfdx{y}{t}}{y}{0}\)</span> (the impact velocity).</p>
